<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>SM Productions LLC | Brand Opportunities</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Brand partnership and sponsorship opportunities with SM Productions LLC in South Florida fashion and live events." />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #151515;
            --surface: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
            --surface-strong: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
            --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            --text: #f4efe4;
            --white: #ffffff;
            --muted: rgba(244,239,228,0.76);
            --faint: rgba(244,239,228,0.44);
            --gold: #d6a43a;
            --gold-soft: #e1b85a;
            --gold-light: #f0cf78;
            --max: 1240px;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
            background: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        a {
            color: inherit;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        img {
            display: block;
            max-width: 100%;
        }

        button {
            font: inherit;
        }

        .page {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: stretch;
        }

        .sidebar {
            width: 280px;
            padding: 28px 24px;
            border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
            background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(214,164,58,0.14), transparent 58%);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 24px;
        }

        .brand-logo {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .brand-logo img {
            height: 46px;
            width: auto;
            object-fit: contain;
        }

        .sidebar h1 {
            font-family: "Outfit", sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.45rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.12em;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .sidebar p {
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(214,164,58,0.6);
            color: var(--gold-light);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.14em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .sidebar-nav {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 6px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .sidebar-nav a {
            font-size: 0.92rem;
            color: var(--muted);
        }

        .sidebar-nav a:hover {
            color: var(--gold-light);
        }

        .sidebar-footer {
            margin-top: auto;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--faint);
        }

        .content {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 32px 32px 32px 32px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 24px;
        }

        .content-header {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 16px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding-bottom: 18px;
        }

        .content-title {
            max-width: 560px;
        }

        .eyebrow {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.16em;
        }

        .display-title {
            font-family: "Outfit", sans-serif;
            font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3vw, 2.4rem);
            letter-spacing: -0.03em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .display-title span {
            color: var(--gold);
        }

        .content-sub {
            margin-top: 10px;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 0.96rem;
        }

        .actions {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .btn-primary,
        .btn-secondary {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 11px 18px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            font-size: 0.88rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
            border: 1px solid transparent;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: var(--gold);
            color: #111;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: var(--gold-soft);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(214,164,58,0.25);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: transparent;
            border-color: var(--border);
            color: var(--muted);
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            border-color: var(--gold-light);
            color: var(--gold-light);
        }

        .preview-layout {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 2.1fr) minmax(0, 1.4fr);
            gap: 22px;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .pdf-wrapper {
            border-radius: 18px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.03), rgba(255,255,255,0.01));
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
            min-height: 420px;
        }

        .pdf-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 10px 14px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
        }

        .pdf-dots {
            display: flex;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        .pdf-dot {
            width: 9px;
            height: 9px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
        }

        .pdf-dot:first-child {
            background: #ff5f57;
        }

        .pdf-dot:nth-child(2) {
            background: #febc2e;
        }

        .pdf-dot:nth-child(3) {
            background: #28c840;
        }

        .pdf-title {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--muted);
        }

        .pdf-frame {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            min-height: 380px;
            border: none;
            background: #111;
        }

        .summary-card {
            border-radius: 18px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
            padding: 18px 18px 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .summary-card h2 {
            font-family: "Outfit", sans-serif;
            font-size: 1rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.14em;
            color: var(--gold-light);
        }

        .summary-card p {
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 0.92rem;
        }

        .summary-list {
            list-style: none;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        .summary-list li {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--muted);
            padding-left: 14px;
            position: relative;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .summary-list li::before {
            content: "•";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: var(--gold-soft);
        }

        .section-footer {
            margin-top: 12px;
            padding-top: 12px;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .contact-tag {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--faint);
        }

        .contact-tag a {
            color: var(--gold-light);
        }

        @media (max-width: 960px) {
            .page {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            .sidebar {
                width: 100%;
                border-right: none;
                border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
                padding-bottom: 18px;
            }
            .content {
                padding: 20px 18px 24px;
            }
            .preview-layout {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            .pdf-wrapper {
                min-height: 360px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .actions {
                width: 100%;
                justify-content: flex-start;
            }
            .btn-primary,
            .btn-secondary {
                width: 100%;
                justify-content: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="page">
        <aside class="sidebar">
            <a class="brand-logo" href="./main.html">
                <img src="./assets/SM-Logo.png" alt="SM Productions LLC logo" />
            </a>
            <div>
                <span class="badge">Brands & Sponsors</span>
                <h1>Brand Opportunities</h1>
                <p>
                    A concise deck for sponsors and partners who want to understand how SM Productions LLC creates visibility inside South Florida fashion and live events.
                </p>
            </div>
            <nav class="sidebar-nav">
                <a href="./main.html">← Back to Main Site</a>
                <a href="#pdf">View deck</a>
                <a href="#summary">Highlights</a>
            </nav>
            <div class="sidebar-footer">
                SM Productions LLC • South Florida • Fashion Shows & Live Productions
            </div>
        </aside>

        <main class="content">
            <header class="content-header">
                <div class="content-title">
                    <span class="eyebrow">For brands & sponsors</span>
                    <h2 class="display-title">
                        Visibility moments that feel <span>live</span>, local and on-brand.
                    </h2>
                    <p class="content-sub">
                        Use this deck to review partnership tiers, brand activation ideas and how your sponsorship shows up in SM Productions experiences.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="actions">
                    <a class="btn-primary" href="./assets/brands-opportunities.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                        View PDF
                    </a>
                    <a class="btn-secondary" href="./assets/brands-opportunities.pdf" download>
                        Download PDF
                    </a>
                </div>
            </header>

            <section id="pdf" class="preview-layout">
                <div class="pdf-wrapper">
                    <div class="pdf-header">
                        <div class="pdf-dots">
                            <span class="pdf-dot"></span>
                            <span class="pdf-dot"></span>
                            <span class="pdf-dot"></span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="pdf-title">brands-opportunities.pdf</div>
                    </div>
                    <iframe
                        class="pdf-frame"
                        src="./assets/brands-opportunities.pdf"
                        title="SM Productions LLC Brand Opportunities PDF"
                    ></iframe>
                </div>

                <aside id="summary" class="summary-card">
                    <h2>Inside this deck</h2>
                    <p>
                        A quick overview of how SM Productions approaches sponsor visibility,
                        audience connection and live fashion experiences across South Florida.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="summary-list">
                        <li>Positioning of SM Productions LLC as a South Florida fashion platform.</li>
                        <li>Concepts for brand activations and sponsor presence.</li>
                        <li>Audience, event energy and moment-based visibility.</li>
                        <li>Ways to collaborate on upcoming shows and productions.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="section-footer">
                        <span class="contact-tag">
                            Ready to talk? Email <a href="mailto:smproductions2026@gmail.com">smproductions2026@gmail.com</a>
                        </span>
                    </div>
                </aside>
            </section>
        </main>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
